| Tier | Price | Features | Target |
|------|-------|----------|--------|
| **Free** | $0/forever | All core features | Viral growth |
| **Pro** | $8/user/mo | Analytics, priority support | Power users |
| **Team** | $15/user/mo | Admin console, policies | Studios |
| **Enterprise** | Custom | SSO, audit logs, SLA | Large orgs |

**Why These Prices:**
- 40-60% below Dropbox ($15), Box ($20), Frame.io ($25)
- P2P = 95% lower infrastructure cost = sustainable margins
- Free tier drives viral adoption (every share = potential new user)

## Messaging Don'ts

| Don't Say | Why | Say Instead |
|-----------|-----|-------------|
| "Disrupting the cloud" | Cliché | "Direct peer-to-peer" |
| "Revolutionary" | Overused | "Simple" or "Fast" |
| "Seamless" | Meaningless | Be specific: "One-click" |
| "Leverage" | Corporate speak | "Use" |
| "Best-in-class" | Unverifiable | Cite specific metric |

